<h2 id="what-is-foundationalism">What is Foundationalism?</h2>

<p>According to Foundationalism, our justified beliefs comprise of a foundation and a superstructure. The superstructure rests one the foundation. Any beliefs belonging to the foundation are <em>basic</em> while those belonging to the superstructure are <em>nonbasic</em> and receive justification from the foundation.</p>
